RESPONSE: Please see the attached Driver’s License. 
5. Please produce color copies of all photographs and/or video recordings that are in 
your possession (including the constructive possession of employees, agents, or representatives), and 
that reflect: (a) the scene of the subject crash as it existed in the time after the collision; (b) any of 
the vehicles involved in the crash at any time on or after the date of the collision; or (c) any injuries 
to persons involved in the collision. 
RESPONSE: Please see the attached Photographs. 

10 
 
6. For each and every insurance policy identified in your Response to Interrogatory 
No. 2, above, please produce complete copies of all such insurance policies, including without 
limitation,  any  and  all:  terms  of  the  policy,  references  to  policy  limits,  declaration  pages, 
amendments, endorsements, riders, exclusions, or add-ons. 
RESPONSE: Please see the attached Declarations Page. 
7. Please produce complete copies of all title documents and/or ownership documents 
that identify the owner of the vehicle you were occupying at the time of the collision.  
RESPONSE: Please see the attached Certificate of Title. 
8. Please produce all documents that you, or your attorney, representatives or agents, 
receive in response to all non-party subpoenas issued by you, or your attorney, representatives or 
