all notes, recordings, photographs, or other recorded information gathered by the experts that are 
relied upon in forming their opinions and conclusions in this smatter. 
RESPONSE: This  Defendant  will  supplement in  this  response  in  accordance  with  the 
Alabama Rules of Civil Procedure, if necessary. 

