 10. Please produce all reports made to, by, or on behalf of any governmental agency, 
police, or law enforcement official regarding the wreck that is the subject of this lawsuit, including 
any entry on an accident register.  
RESPONSE: Objection, in part. In so far as this request seeks information gathered in 
anticipation of litigation, such documents are protected be the attorney-client privilege and 
work  product  doctrine.  In  so  far  as  this  request  seeks  information,  not  gathered  in 
anticipation for litigation, see attached Accident Report. 
