DEFINITIONS

Unless otherwise indicated, the following definitions shall be applicable to these Discovery Requests:

1.	"YOU" and "YOUR" shall mean: the Defendant(s) to whom these discovery requests are directed, including their attorneys, experts (including without limitation, their expert’s contractors, subcontractors, agents and employees), employees, agents, representatives and all other persons acting on their behalf.

