14.	The term "REPORT" or "REPORTS" shall include, without limitation: any CORRESPONDENCE or COMMUNICATION wherein there is contained any criticism, question, complaint, claim, notice, issue, grievance, conclusion, belief, opinion, concern, charge or protest, whether written or oral, and whether noted, observed or communicated by a person not employed by Defendant or noted, observed or communicated by a person employed by the Defendant.

