MOTION TO CONTINUE CERTIFICATE OF READINESS DEADLINE 
 
 
 COMES  NOW,  Plaintiff  ERIKA  COREY  TURNER,  by  and  through  her 
undersigned attorney, and files this Motion to Continue Certificate of Readiness 
Deadline in this matter. In support thereof, Plaintiff states as follows: 
1. Plaintiff’s Certificate of Readiness in this matter is currently set to be 
filed by October 31, 2025, per this Court’s Pre-Trial Order. (Doc. 5). 
2. Plaintiff has had ongoing medical treatment leading to the delay of 
depositions being taken in this matter.  
3. Depositions have been scheduled. 
4. Plaintiff requests the deadline to file their Certificate of Readiness in 
this matter be extended by 180 days.  
5. Defense Counsel has stated they are unopposed to this Motion.  
WHEREFORE, premises considered, Plaintiff requests this Honorable Court 
grant this Motion to Continue Certificate of Readiness Deadline by 180 days. 
Respectfully Submitted this 10
th
 day of October 2025.  
