CIVIL SUBPOENA FOR PRODUCTION OF DOCUMENTS UNDER RULE 45 
 
Grelot Physical Therapy 
Attn: Custodian of Records 
5901 Grelot Rd., Bldg. B, Suite B. 
Mobile, AL 36609 
 
 You  are  hereby commanded  to  do  each  of  the  following  acts  at  the  instance  of  the 
Defendant, within fifteen (15) days after service of this subpoena: 
 
1. That you produce and permit petitioner to obtain possession of, inspect and/or 
to copy the following documents or things: 
    
 A. All records, writings, documents, reports or other written material contained 
in  your  file,  in  your  possession  or  under  your  control,  and  copies  of  all 
reports of x-rays, bone scans, CT scans, or other radiographic or ultrasonic 
diagnostic tools, relative to any examination, care and treatment rendered 
to the following individual: 
 
PATIENT: ERIKA COREY TURNER 
DOB: 6/05/1965 
 
 B. All  writings,  business  records  or  other  written  material  contained  in  your 
file,  in  your  possession  or  under  your  control  relative  to  fees,  statements, 
bills or invoices for any charges made to the above individual or to any third 
party  for  said  patient''s care.    These  records  are  also  to  include  records  of 
any  payments  made  by  the  patient  or  any  third  party,  including,  but  not 
limited to, insurance payments or benefits. 
 
 2. This  request  is  to  encompass  any, and  all  records,  which  are  in  any  way 
related  to  the  above-named  patient  and  should  not  be  considered  or 
construed as a limited request. 
